extends layout.pug


block content 
  article.grid-container.portfolio-intro
    div

      h1.lobsterFont My Portfolio

      p.lead.text-light
        | These projects were completed during the 5 first units of the Techdegree Program. The Full Stack JavaScript Techdegree is meant to train students in HTML, CSS, JavaScript, NodeJS and Express, and this lets me practice and show off my mastery of these fundamental skills.
  article.grid-container.portfolio-index
    
    .grid-x.grid-margin-x.small-up-2.medium-up-2.large-up-3

      each val, index in project
        .cell            
            a(href= "project/" + index)
                .boundary
                    img.thumbnail.projectImg(src= project[index].image_urls[0])
                h5.letterPopUp= project[index].project_name